text: Joaquín Zeballos Machado (born 30 November 1996) is a Uruguayan professional footballer who plays as a forward for Spanish team Barcelona B on loan from Girona. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:People from Maldonado Department Category:Association football forwards Category:Uruguayan footballers Category:Deportivo Maldonado players Category:Huracán F.C. players Category:Juventud de Las Piedras players Category:Girona FC players Category:FC Barcelona B players Category:Uruguayan Primera División players Category:Uruguayan Segunda División players Category:Segunda División players Category:Segunda División B players Category:Uruguayan expatriate footballers Category:Uruguayan expatriate sportspeople in Spain
